A technology firm with strength in the real estate sector, Vegah has unveiled an application that boosts operations in the industry.
   
Known as VinoFacility App, it is a unique identifier for individual industry actors and traces their success. The VinoFacility Web App promotes the green environment by subscribing to cloud computing to secure client consultant activities.
  
According to Vegah, Apps like VinoFacility enable the estate industry in Nigeria to keep pace with international best practices with fewer building collapses.
  
The Operations Director of the DUKAN Group, owners of Vegah, Chinedu Amadi, explained that the unveiling of the app coincided with the fifth anniversary of the firm in the estate development market. 